20:06.880 --> 20:09.790
♪ You never do things
just because ♪

20:11.880 --> 20:13.420
♪ And I can watch you leave ♪

20:13.420 --> 20:15.040
♪ Take your coat and your keys ♪

20:15.040 --> 20:18.040
♪ And I wouldn't care
where you go ♪

20:18.040 --> 20:19.960
♪ But the hell of it is ♪

20:19.960 --> 20:22.000
♪ I love you even when I don't ♪

