37:17.380 --> 37:20.670
- Miss Barnes, you okay?

37:34.330 --> 37:36.170
- Juliette.

37:38.380 --> 37:39.620
- Why did you leave?

37:39.620 --> 37:42.500
- I didn't, sweetie.

37:42.500 --> 37:45.880
I would never leave you.

37:45.880 --> 37:47.080
But I can't come home.

37:47.080 --> 37:48.670
- No!

37:48.670 --> 37:51.500
- Oh, come here.

37:51.500 --> 37:54.830
Listen, okay?

37:54.830 --> 37:58.290
You will always be my jewel.

37:58.290 --> 38:02.040
And I will always
be watching over you.

38:02.040 --> 38:06.380
Whatever wonderful thing you do,

38:06.380 --> 38:10.710
and it will be wonderful,

38:10.710 --> 38:12.420
cause that's just who you are.

38:17.620 --> 38:20.380
Just know, I will be there.

